data.description: NEW ROOF INSTALLED, PRICE DROP AND 2% CONCESSIONS BEING OFFERED! Discover this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home located in Verde Village Unit 4. The upgraded kitchen and bathrooms showcase modern design and functionality. Step into the landscaped backyard, where a mature tree provides shade and tranquility, accompanied by a delightful playset that will be an instant hit with family and friends. Embrace the serene surroundings and fish in the community pond with walking path, that is just around the corner. This home presents a unique opportunity to enjoy both a well-appointed interior and the natural beauty of the nearby amenities. Property boasts plenty of parking and huge storage shed. Join the voluntary POA ($60 annually) or pay per visit at the community clubhouse and pool.
